rows.label: bf07410150_0020
rows.name: Is it dedication or what would you call it?

rows.label: bf07410150_0030
rows.name: What? Did you come to confess your love to me?

rows.label: bf07410150_0040
rows.name: Are you an idiot? Go die.

rows.label: bf07410150_0050
rows.name:
Yeah, yeah.
I'll do that... eventually.

rows.label: bf07410150_0070
rows.name:
You know, the Marsanes is the last
Iiran warship.

rows.label: bf07410150_0080
rows.name: I'm readying it for battle with non-human opponents.

rows.label: bf07410150_0100
rows.name: That should be obvious, don't you think?

rows.label: bf07410150_0140
rows.name: By the way, what do you need?

rows.label: bf07410150_0150
rows.name:
F-food's ready.
Eat it before it gets cold.

rows.label: bf07410150_0160
rows.name:
Oh, you came all the way just for that?
I can feel the love.

rows.label: bf07410150_0170
rows.name: I'm seriously going to kill you, you bastard.

rows.label: bf07410150_0180
rows.name:
Okay, got it.
Well. I'd better go and eat this delicious spread.
